review_blob: Great overall beer, good for when you dont feel like drinking the normal party beer. A bit more expensive, but really does the job. unlike most beers, it starts to taste less good as you go on, so i suggest drinking six of these and then heading to a 12pack of natty light or ice.. but if you go the ice route, be careful or youll be bent over in front of the toilet..
God I love this beer. I used to think it was horrible but now its like a part of me. If this beers production was ever halted, id probably quit drinking..
